These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, balloon-flower
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, lilac, blood-red
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, animation, time-travel
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, havana, pall-mall
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, musician, freelancer
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, spanish
 1. the spanish is the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the freelancer is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the spanish is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is the person who likes blue##1
 6. the brazilian is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 7. the baccarat-smoker is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person who likes lilac is in the middle##1
 9. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the photographer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3     |
| Flower      | lily | balloon-flower        | daisy |
| Color          | blood-red    | lilac        | blue    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel        | superhero        | animation    |
| Cigar           | pall-mall        | baccarat    | havana   |
| Job         | musician    | freelancer | photographer |
| Nationality     | egyptian     | brazilian          | spanish     |

