.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-2::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, onion, spinach
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, ivory, green
3 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, fish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, oliveros, cain
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, lemonade
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, mah-jongg
1. the person who likes aquamarine is the cain-smoker##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes green##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
5. the person eating apple is the person playing whist##1
6. the cain-smoker is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
8. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
9. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Food         | spinach    | apple     | onion            |
| Color           | ivory | aquamarine | green |
| Pet   | mouse    | guinea-pig      | fish             |
| Cigar   | davidoff | cain     | oliveros             |
| Beverage         | mirinda  | lemonade       | milk           |
| Game     | mah-jongg     | whist   | bridge            |

