The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, country, metal
There 3 different types of food: peach, apricot, mango
House: farmhouse, futuristic, cape-cod
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, juice
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, ivory, blood-red
1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating peach##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
6. the person drinking juice is the person who likes chestnut##1
7. the person drinking sprite is the person eating apricot##1
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
9. the futuristic house is the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |
| Flower         | iris  | balloon-flower     | azalea    |
| Music-Genre           | country | jazz  | metal |
| Food   | mango       | peach | apricot      |
| House   | farmhouse     | cape-cod      | futuristic     |
| Beverage           | juice          | iced-tea      | sprite   |
| Color     | chestnut          | blood-red       | ivory    |

