The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, taxi, bike
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, dubstep, disco
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 4. the vegafina-smoker is in the middle##1
