 7. the fan of disco is the person drinking milk##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
10. the person driving the taxi is the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |
| Sport          | skateboarding | cycling | sailing        |
