The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, september, october
3 different games are played: poker, chess, whist
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, fuchsia, apricot
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, roller, train
3 different pets are kept: mouse, frog, hedgehog
 1. the person playing whist is the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes apricot is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the wooden house##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is the person playing poker##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 8. the futuristic house is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the right of the wooden house##1
10. the person who likes aquamarine is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| House      | futuristic    | wooden     | modern         |
| Birthday          | may  | october    | september         |
| Game           | chess | whist | poker          |
| Color   | aquamarine    | apricot      | fuchsia        |
| Transport   | train     | scooter     | roller          |
| Pet         | hedgehog    | mouse | frog |

