.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, chess
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, comedy, spy
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski, bus
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, april, june
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, analyst, firefighter
1. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1
2. the firefighter is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the analyst is the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
9. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| Game          | backgammon          | chess      | mah-jongg      |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate        | juice | iced-tea      |
| Movie-Genre   | western          | comedy        | spy       |
| Transport   | roller       | jet-ski   | bus      |
| Birthday           | april           | june      | february         |
| Job         | firefighter | dressmaker    | analyst |

 